Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the effectiveness of various machine learning methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper explores the potential for future research, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category.
